<article class="node node--type-page node--view-mode-full clearfix">
  <header>
    
        
      </header>
  <div class="node__content clearfix">
    


            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="row">
<div class="col-md-4">
<figure role="group" class="caption caption-drupal-media align-left">
<div>
  
  
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Image</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/full_width/public/images/63977813-9E15-4FC3-89FE-BB808F3EE25D.jpeg?itok=Q9qdZn8G" width="2048" height="2901" alt="Out on the Ravn" class="image-style-full-width">


</div>
          </div>

</div>
<figcaption>On a local road ride</figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<p>I got serious about bicycle riding in 2004. I had been working a desk job for 12 years and slowly but surely putting on weight. At first I was just into mountain biking but soon good a road bike and started doing long rides with friends. The eventually led to bicycle touring which soon became my passion.&nbsp;</p>
<p>These days I still try and make the weekly club rides and get out on a tour whenever I can.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<figure role="group" class="caption caption-drupal-media align-right">
